# No Cursor Agent Trailer

**CRITICAL RULE**: You must NEVER include the text `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>` in any file, page, or Git commit message.

When making git commits, ensure that this trailer is stripped out if it is generated by default.

```bash
# ❌ BAD
git commit -m "My commit message
Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>"

# ✅ GOOD
git commit -m "My commit message"
```
